Title: Veg Biryani
Description: Prepared with fragrant basmati rice, vegetables, flavorful spices, and occasionally nuts and dried fruits.

Title: Bean Burger
Description: A vegan burger prepared with mashed black beans, kidney beans, vegetables, and different seasonings.

Title: Vegetarian Sandwich
Description: A vegetarian sandwich prepared with cheese, tomatoes, avocados and peppers.

Title: Vegan Momos
Description: A type of dumpling originating from China. Its filling with consists of ginger, cumin, garlic and cilantro.
